title: Hectopascal
summary: Hectopascal ManhwaPark Han-jun, once called a legend, was frustrated because he had nothing to lose anymore is given a huge amount of money. An eye for an eye. An eye for a tooth! I’ll make you pay for what I’ve gone through! As his rage explodes, he’ll get his sweet revenge and make them pay as much as they deserve! 헥토파스칼, Hectopascals
